data.description: Welcome home!! On the main level of this stunning 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home you will find an office/bonus room, formal dining room, spacious kitchen, and an informal dining space that opens from the kitchen into the living room with it's gorgeous fireplace. Upstairs, your master suite is half of the upper level, with it's own sitting area and a stunning master bathroom. Separated from the master suite by an upstairs bonus room are the additional bedrooms and laundry. On the outside, you can enjoy low maintenance brick and vinyl siding home and its incredible fenced back yard with a seating area, playground, grill area, and a covered back porch. This home has so much to offer but don’t take my word for it, schedule your appointment to see it TODAY! All information deemed reliable, but not guaranteed.
